All Implemented Interfaces:
AuctionEventListener, Parameterizable, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
public class CumulativeTraderDistributionPanel
extends TraderDistributionPanel

Displays the number of traders registered respectively with specialists. Different from TraderDistributionPanel that displays all daily plots, this panel shows the average daily trader registration over time and that for the current day.
